> 
> At the risk of making bugzilla just a little too annoying, if you find
> yourself having to manually remove the cc in selected bug entries just
> because you participated in the thread at some point.
At least with bugzilla you have an option to remove yourself from the
CC list.  With a mailing list thread you could get CCed just the same
and there is nothing you can do about it apart from raising a complaint
on the list.
